quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  21,82,"Men elti immorde e Seytanuuji Й—in, Й—in Й—i no mutana mo ka maaje Й—i yaltina lu'ulu'uuje e tanaa mu'un, hiЙ—i golla kadi ko wonaa Й—um immorde e golle wano mahugol, Men laatike ko Men ReenuЙ“e limoore majji e golle majji, hay e huunde e Й—um fuutataako Men."
  21,83,"JaЕӢtii -an NulaaЙ—o- fillayee fii Ayyuuba (yo o his), tuma nde o noddunoo Joomi makko O Senike tuma nde jarrabuyee on heЙ“unoo mo ko o wi'uЙ—o: "Ko an yo Jooma, min dey mi hennaama Гұaw e waaseede Й“eynguure nden, ko An woni ЖҒurЙ—o Yurmeende yurmeteeЙ“e Й“en fow, martin e am Й—um ko heЙ“i lam"."
  21,84,"Men jaabi toraare makko nden, Men ittini mo ko heЙ“i mo kon immorde e lorra, Men okkiti mo ko o hattinoo kon immorde e Й“eynguure makko e geЙ—al Й“e makko, Men okkiti mo wano maЙ“Й“e wonndude e maЙ“Й“e, kala Й—um Men waЙ—irii Й—um Yurmeende immorde ka Amen, e waaju wonannde kala Й—oftorЙ—o Alla dewal; fii yo o munГұor wano Ayyuuba munГұornoo non."
  21,85,"JaЕӢtii -an NulaaЙ—o- Ismaa'iila e Idriisa e Jalkifli (yo Й“e his), gooto-kala e maЙ“Й“e ko e munГұiiЙ“e jarrabuyee Й“en Й“e jeyaa, e hoore daranagol kon ko Alla fawi Й“e."
  21,86,"Men naadi Й“e e nder Yurmeende Amen, Men waЙ—i Й“e AnnabaaЙ“e, Men naadi Й“e ka Aljanna, pellet, kamЙ“e ko Й“e jeyaaЙ“e e jeyaaЙ“e Alla moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e gollirЙ“e Й“en Й—oftaare Joomi maЙ“Й“e nden, tawi gunndooji maЙ“Й“e e kene maЙ“Й“e no moЖҙЖҙi."
  21,87,"JaЕӢto -an NulaaЙ—o- fillayee fii jom linngii ngil Yuunusa (yo o his), tum nde o yahunoo ko aldaa e duЕӢayee(sakkitgol immorde ka Joomi makko ko o tikkanЙ—o yimЙ“e makko Й“en sabu duumagol maЙ“Й“e e geddi Й—in, o sikki wonnde Menen Men Й“ittinan-taa mo; leptirgol fii ko o yahi kon, o jarriboraa saЙ—tude Й“itteede e dummbeede fewndo linngil ngil moЙ—unoo mo, o noddi ka nder niЙ“e reedu linngil ngil e maayo ngon e jemma on; ko o qirritiiЙ—o bakkaatu makko on tuubuЙ—o ka Alla immorde e Й—um, o wi'i: "ReweteeЙ—o e goonga alaa tanaa MaaЙ—a, A Senike A LaaЙ“ii, min dey mi wonii jeyaaЙ—o e tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"."
  21,88,"Men jaabinani mo, Men danndiri mo immorde e saЙ—teende suno ngon yaltinngol mo ka nder niЙ“e, e ka nder reedu linngil ngil, ko yeru no Yuunusa danndiranoo nii e ndee saЙ—teende makko Й—oo Men danndirta gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en si Й“e yanii e saЙ—teende Й“e torike Alla."
  21,89,"JaЕӢto -an NulaaЙ—o- fillayee Jakariyaa (yo o his) tuma nde o noddunoo Joomi makko Senayee wonanii Mo o maaki: "Jooma, wata A accan ko mi teelЙ—o hara mi alaa Й“iЙ—Й—o, ko An woni ЖҒurЙ—o MoЖҙЖҙude heddotooЙ“e Й“en, arsikam Й“iЙ—Й—o mo no heddoo Й“aawo am"."
  21,90,"Men jaabinani mo toraare makko nden, Men Okki mo Yahyaa Й“iЙ—Й—o, Men moЖҙЖҙini sonnaajo makko on, o wonti jibinoowo Й“aawo hari o laatinoke dimaro, pellet, Jakariyaa e sonna makko e geЙ—aljo makko on Й“e laatinoke hiЙ“e heГұoo faade e gollugol moЖҙЖҙi Й—in, Й“e laatinoke hiЙ“e nodda Men hara ko Й“e rerЙ—uЙ“e ko woni kon ka Amen immorde mbarjaari ndin, hara ko Й“e huluЙ“e kon ko woni ka Amen immorde e lepte Й—en, Й“e woniino yankinaniiЙ“e Men."